items.title: YouTube to be included in Australia's teen social media ban
items.description: The Australian government says the world-first ban is aimed at protecting youth from online harm.

items.title: Outcry after German zoo culled baboons due to overcrowding
items.description: The zoo in Nuremberg said it knew many people would be "upset" or "infuriated" by the decision.

items.title: Greece claims 'invasion' in Crete as it tries to halt asylum on Med route
items.description: Greek migration minister Thanos Plevris says his country faces a "state of emergency".

items.title: Russian soldiers scammed and robbed of war cash on return from Ukraine
items.description: A number of cases emerge of servicemen targeted for their salaries and pay-offs by government officials.

items.title: Why plane turbulence is really becoming more frequent - and more severe
